<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>HUASING.XYZ</title><link>/</link><description>TEST ALL</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>/logo.png</url><title>HUASING.XYZ</title><link>/</link></image><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 19 Dec 2020 10:07:34 +0806</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Sat, 19 Dec 2020 10:07:34 +0806</pubDate><item><title>通过宏禁止Excel文件的保存</title><link>/archives/do-not-save-my-excel/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在工作中，一些Excel表格只用于查询和临时修改，实际并不需要修改保存。为避免一时手残给保存了，就需要做出限制。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VBA&lt;strong&gt;设计模式&lt;/strong&gt;下，在ThisWorkbook中插入VBA代码：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Private Sub Workbook_BeforeClose(Cancel As Boolean)
Me.Saved = True
End Sub

Private Sub Workbook_BeforeSave(ByVal SaveAsUI As Boolean, Cancel As Boolean)
Cancel = True
End Sub&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;保存后返回Excel即可。&lt;/p&gt;
